<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HabitToHelp</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <!--Google font added-->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"></head>        
</head>
<body>
  <div class='wrapper'>    
    <div class="menu">
      <a href="/" class="logo">HabitToHelp</a>

    </div>
    <div class='container'>    
      <div class='main left'>
        <div class="wrapperLeft">
          <p>Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit, sed quia non numquam eius modi tempora incidunt ut labore et dolore magnam aliquam quaerat voluptatem. Ut enim ad minima veniam.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    <div class='main right'>
      <div class="wrapperRight">
        <h1 class="logo">Welcome to HabitToHelp</h1>
        <p>You are now a user, please login to start tracking your habits.</p>
        <section> 
          <form action="/signUpSuccess" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                name="email"
                class="form-control"
                placeholder="Enter Email address"
                value="<%= typeof email != 'undefined' ? email : '' %>"
              />
              <input
                type="password"
                id="password"
                name="password"
                class="form-control"
                placeholder="Enter Password"
                value="<%= typeof password != 'undefined' ? password : '' %>"
              />
            </div>
            <a class="forgotPassword" href="#">Forgot password?</a>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block submitButton">Sign in</button>
          </form>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>   
</div>      
<%- include("globalElements/footer") %>
</body>
</html>